snippet.title: Release Date Reveal | Overwatch 2
snippet.description:
#Overwatch2 arrives October 4 as an always-on, always-evolving, free to play experience. Team up in a new 5v5 PvP experience, featuring new and reworked heroes, new maps and modes, and more.

Learn more about the newest tank hero to join the roster: Junker Queen, Overwatch 2's live service model and seasonal content plan during the Overwatch 2 Reveal Event livestream June 16 at 10 AM PT.

snippet.title: Overwatch 2 | Junker Queen Deep Dive (Reveal Event Clip)
snippet.description:
Soe Gschwind sits down with Overwatch 2 Art Director Dion Rogers, Narrative Designer Miranda Moyer, and Cinematic Director Ben Dai to learn more about the newest tank hero to join the roster -- the Australian-born ruler of Junkertown: the Junker Queen. Plus, meet additional members of the development team who discuss what went into bringing Junker Queen to life, including character design, weapons, abilities and more! 

Play as Junker Queen when Overwatch 2 arrives October 4 or in the upcoming Overwatch 2 beginning June 28 on PC and select consoles. For more information on the beta and to sign up, visit https://playoverwatch.com/beta/  

Watch the full reveal event for more information on Overwatch 2: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dTUX1zacoZ4  

#Overwatch2 arrives October 4th free to play on Windows® PC and Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, PlayStation®5, PlayStation®4, and Nintendo Switch™ consoles. 
_
